My Angel Up Above


My angel up above
In the clouds she is looking down
Shining bright with beauty and love

Her beauty so radiant 
Her love so divine
And to think
I used to call her mine

Now with this gun to my head
I fight to pull the trigger
Wanting to join her on that cloud
But not wanting to leave this earth

Pressing hard into my skull
Boring a hole to my brain
The barrel feels so cold
Tears pouring out of my eyes
This pain is getting old

Her beauty so radiant 
Her love so divine
And to think
I used to call her mine

I just want to be 
With my angel up above



ok so this one is a little bit morbid, but its not talking about suicide. yes i know that is the theme of the song , but the underlying theme is that this dude would do anything to get to this girl, to make her notice him, even something as radical as killing himself. not to worry though, its just a song, not an omen that i am gonna do anything. let me know what you think. 
-Mule-

Ok so i havent updated in a while. there is a reason for that. ive been reall busy lately and i havent had time. plus this thing has gotten me into too much trouble with putting my feelings out there for everyone to see.  so im done with this. you can beg and plead all you want to, but im stopping. no more. im cutting it off right now before anything gets worse. so for the last time, Peace.

-Mark-

I KILLED A POSSUM!!!!!!! i was on my way home from abbotts house and a possum ran out in front of me and i killed him. that makes me sad. but i am feeling good regardless because i hung outn with my man abbott mitchell tonight. we watched the chevelle dvd and played guitars. i know i know im a drummer, but i can mess around on the guitar if i want to.  but thats all i got for now. peace.

-Mule-

so i havent updated in a couple days, so i figure ill give you a little teaser. so this is how my day went........................................tune in tomorrow for the rest of the story. have a nice night.

-Mule-

hey everybody, guess what??????? im a dad. at work today the snake eggs that i have been incubating, they hatched!!!!!! im so excited. i have 4 little baby snowkatee corn snakes they are so pretty. they are a mixed breed of 2 of the snakes we have a t work. our snow corn and okatee corn. the babies are light and dark gray and so cute. bu they did try to bite me though, which was not cool i might add. i cared for them and they go and try to hurt me. oh well natural instinct. thats my exciting news for the day. everybody have a good night.

-Mark-
my weekend was great! i hope everyone elses was good too. have a great week cause i know mine will be!!!!!

ok so i dont know why im hyper, i just am. i had a really good day and i went to church tonight. church always makes me hyper. i dont know why though. oh and guess what i found out!!!!!! i have to run sound all by myself next wednesday. AHHHH!!!!!!!!! i know how to do the sound board but i dont know how to switch all the screens and stuff like that. so im kinda flipping out. i hope someone is there that can do that. cause ill be messed up badly if i have to do that by myself. things will be poping up on the screen that dont need to be there and the dvd will be running when its supposed to be media shout, everything will be screwed up. OH NO!!!! oh well, i guess ill just have to fake that i know what im doing. no one will know....till i screw up that is. anyway, im headed to the wonderful bed. peace out

-Mark-

ok so the reason i am confused is this, i went to Coldstone's icecream shop tonight and there was this guy behind the counter who was obviously gay, and he was hitting on me. like what is it about me that throws off peoples gaydar. i get lots of gay guys hitting on me. and even some straight people think im gay at first. i dont know what it is about me. is it because i am well groomed or at least look a little bit cleaner than most guys. that just bugs the mess out of me. oh well thats my dilema for the day. peace out!

-Mark-

so atlanta was alot of fun. im glad to be home, but i wanted to see how much more atlanta had to offer. oh well. its good to be back sleeping in my own bed because shareing a bed with abbott wasnt cutting it. yes i shared a bed with another guy.....GET OFF MY BACK!!!!! it was funny cause we were both like if you touch me in any way improper i will kill you even if you are sleeping. haha. it was funny. the braves game was kinda disappointing. long story short, the lost 8-0. the marlins kicked their butts. anyway, we went to a water park on friday and a go-kart and putt-putt place. the putt-putt sucked. it was horrible. the greens were all messed up and everything. and the go-karts were cool tiil this kid got me in trouble for bumping and was totally his fault. i got in trouble because i was the bigger one and i didnt even do anything the little booger cut me off. i finally smoked him though. saturday we went to six flags over georgia. that place was awesome. the superman is the best ride EVER!!!!!!! it was so cool. on sunday we went to this gigundous church. im talking 5 cameras filming the service and projecting it onto screens placed up high so the balcony could see the service. and our group was put on the screens. woo hoo!!!!then we came home straight from the service and i was really tired but i could go to sleep cause i had an energy drink called vault and that made me wired. we didnt get home till about 12:00am and i didnt leave the church till about 12:30. so i was really tired. and it didnt help that my room didnt go to bed till about 1:30 every night.

anyway im getting tired and i have to go to work in the morning so, peace and hair grease as dolvin would say.

-Mark-
Atalanta baby!!!!!!!!! thrusday to sunday. Leave me some love for when i get home.

ok so i really havent spilled my guts out on this but once or twice so here goes. i was at bible study tonight and allison walked in the room for drama practice afterward. everytime i see her i want to throw up. its horrible. my stomache turns in knots and i just get so nauseated, hence the little guy throwing up. like everytime i think about her i feel this way. i hate it. i just wish it would go away. i wish that i would have never asked her out, i wish that i never had even met her. i just want my life to go back to normal. back to the way i want it to be. but it will never be the way i want it to be. it will always be God's way. i cant have my way because my way is not always the best way. only God knows whats best for mei guess i just have to go with the flow of things and hope i dont get swept up. i just keep praying that it will go away, but its not. i  guess i still feel like this for a reason because there is a reason for everything. i just dont know what it is yet. hopefully ill figure it out sometime. either that or get over it because i need to move on. im trying to move on, but somehow it just isnt working. i mean anna is great, i like her alot. somehow i just cant get my mind away from the whole allison situation. i keep going over in my head what happened and where it went wrong, but i just cant figure it out. why are girls so complicated?????? i just wish that everything were so much easier. and that girls would just be up front with you and tell you what they are saying instead of making some sort of weird game out of it. or maybe its us guys. maybe we are so stupid that we just dont get anything. you know what its prolly that girls think we are smarter than what we really are and just talk like they are talking to a person of the same sex. its really confusing and girls need to take the time to think about what they say before they say it. so many hearts will go unbroken and so many things will only have to be said once.

now that youve heard me rant and rave and now that i have done that, i feel a little bit better. so on that note i will be going to bed. peace!

-Mark-

wow, awesome weekend. it was real, it was fun, it was real fun. i did a whole lot of stuff. first of all my illegal bird died and i had to bury him on friday after work. :( saturday was pretty cool even though i had to work all day with my #4 casey. you know what i mean. we had no one come into the museum from 9-1 it was great. the day really perked up when anna came to see me. i was so happy that she stopped by. after worked i went to pick anna up for dinner with my family. scary!!! dinner went really well though. my parents liked anna a lot. she'll be back from camp on fourth of july weekend and we are gonna go see the fireworks. sunday i had to go listen to dad preach for fathers day. after church we went to golden corral for lunch. im still full. in the afternoon i went with josh, ryan, and daniel to rocky mount for a fun filled time at the mall. later me josh and abbott played raquet ball till about 10:30 at night. it was great. i love my friends.

well since its 11:45 im going to bed. later punks!

-Mark-

long day. pretty fun night. watched some movies with the boys. original batman. what what!! any way i have a long day tomorrow and i need my beauty sleep. catch ya later!

-Mark-

man where to start. ok so i wake up yesterday morning, its just another normal day nothing exciting going on. then 10:30 rolls around and the fedex guy comes. and he brings me my new drums!!!!!!!! im so excited!!! so i tear the boxes smack apart to see what they look like. oh boy are they beautiful. BLACK SPARKLE!!!!!! the bad thing is i couldnt do anything but look at them because i had to go to work. but as im on the way out of the house there is an American Kestrel on the bottom step of our deck and she appeared to be hurt. so guess what....i caught it. and for those of you dummies out there a kestrel is a raptor. and no thats not a dinosaur. its a bird of prey. and why couldnt i just say bird of prey, well thats because i wanted to toy with your little minds. HAHAHAHAHA!!!!!! anyway, i caught the bird and took it to work, long story short we couldnt keep the bird at work and now shes at my house and im nursing her back to health so that we can release her again. now that was all just yeterday.

today i put the drums together!!!! they look great. abbott came over and we play a little bit. and they sound better than they look. its awesome. and the bird is doing much better. so that was my past 2 days. now im going to sleep.

-Mark-

long day. complete with a good long work out at the end to relieve all the stress. i did cramp a little while i was on the treadmill but i worked it out. my abs are gonna be sore tomorrow too. 100 crunches on the crunch machine with an extra 100 pounds. hurt city baby. thats about all i have fo today. so peace and hair grease ( thats for you Dolvin).

-Mark-

umm not much to write about today. church, chilling at the house, care groups, and talking to anna. oh i didnt update yesterday so ill tell you what happened then. it is much more exciting.

so i had to cut grass in the morning. i know not exciting, but just wait. then i had a drum lesson from 2-3. then i went to a PARTAY for my best bud Josh. it was great. chasing chickens and ripped pants. ramping the bikes and the clown bike. then Star Wars at 10 at night. yes this is the 4th time seeing it. and by golly i will see it again. prolly with anna. or by myself, i dont know.

but thats all i got for now. so ill see everyone later.

-Mark-

wow, long week and im glad its over. i am sooo tired and wore smack out its not even funny. im glad i have the day off tomorrow. i actually get to sleep in somewhat. i do have to get up and cut the grass though. and i need a hair cut. and i have a drum lesson. and i need to go to the gym. wow, maybe i wont get to sleep in tomorrow. maybe i should go to sleep now. NAH!!!! ill stay up nice and late. till like 2. no i wont because then youll start to see this lugfihregfikhreoitghreghjqeoirghreqoi;kkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkk. haha that wouldnt be to good. then people wouldnt read my post because it just keeps going like kkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkkk. wow i think i do need to go to sleep now cause im just rambling now. you might think its funny or maybe you think its annoying. i dont know? im not you. and now i will go to sleep. Peace!

-Mark-

So my day was a little better today because a certain some one wasnt at work. and so i didnt get upset all day. YAY me!!!! so the weeks almost over and im so happy about that. and i get paid tomorrow. WOOHOO!!!!! i really need the money now cause i just spent 1200 bucks for a new drum set, cymbals and a throne. yes a throne, i could say a seat, but everyone knows that drummers are the kings and thats why we sit on thrones. HAHAHA!!!!!!!!! anyway, i should be getting it in about 2-3 weeks. im so excited! the reason i am getting a new set is because my old one sounds like a bunch of plastic trash cans put together. so needless to say, i need a new one. i am so thankful for graduation money because without it i would not be getting this new set. so a little bit about the set im getting(yes im already obsessed with it). its a sonor 3003 series. made of maple basswood maple. its color is black sparkle, ohhhh!!! its a five piece set. for all you dummies out there that means five different drums. its got a 20"x17.5" bass drum, 10"x9" tom, 12"x10" tom, 14"x12" suspended floor tom, and a 14"x5.5" wood snare. it also comes with complete hardware. the cymbals im getting are zildjian zxt rock cymbals. ultimate sustain baby!!!

well im tired and have to get up for work in the morning so im going to bed. ill holla at everyone later.

-Mark-

Well my day has been full of crap again. its a good thoing i had church tonight. that really cheered me up. and after church a whole bunch of people went to El Taco Bell. so that was good. im not gonna rant on and on like i did yesterday about how bad my day was, but i will say one thing. im tired of people who think that they own the world and everyone should do as they say. thats all i have to say about that. i hope tomorrow will be better. i am drained already and its only the middle of the week. i just want to sleep for the next 3 days. why 3 i dont know. just a random number. but im rambling now. so that means i need to go to bed. night night everyone.

-M-

this is my time to complain about my bad day. so read on if you dare!!

first off, after going to Kings Dominion i was dead tired and having to go to work at 9 in the morning is not a good thing. so needless to say i woke up late. so i quickly jumped in the shower and ate breakfast. now for some odd reason i just knew today was going to bad. one because i was so tired, and two because i woke up thinking about allison. not good at all!! so i spent most of the day thinking about her and angry at myself cause i was thinking about her. now secondly, the group that came in was horrible. the head teacher was a nasty mean tempered woman who was so mean to the kids and kept telling amy that she was being hateful to her. now the lady had none of her stuff together and she had no idea what was going on. we assigned groups on the bus and when the kids went inside the lady changed the groups around so we had no idea what was going on. and dont even get me started on the kids!!!!!! they tore everything to pieces. so much stuff was broken its not even funny. finally the group left and it was so quiet. thirdly, emily's camp kids were a mess and loud as mess. so i had to help her a little bit with that. needless to say i am drained out. i finally got to leave work and headed off to bible study. i really needed me some Jesus after the day that i had. after bible study i hit the gym to get out some aggression. i ran on the treadmill for a long time while listening to MCR (My Chemical Romance). Rock on MCR!!! pumped some iron too. i really lost alot since the last time i lifted which was like 6 months ago. so i really need to get back into it. which ill get back to my normal weight after a week or so. so im really exhausted now and sore and tired and everything that goes along with that so im off to bed leave me some nice ones.

-Mark-

Man i am soooo tired. being on your feet for 7 hours is not to much fun. especially in sandals. not much arch support! if you were wondering, i was at Kings Dominion. roller coasters out the wazoo baby, YEAH! it was great. i wish we had something like that down here in the crapland of America. it would make it so much more fun. i got a tattoo while i was there too. its a weird little squiggly design. henna by the way. didnt want anyone to freak out. it didnt come out too well though. kinda disappointed that i spent 12 bucks on something that didnt really turn out. oh well, its all good! at least i got somewhat of a tattoo. one step closer to the real thing. a couple more years till im out of the house, and then big tiger right smack on my back. haha just kidding, that would hurt way too much. i like pain, but not that much. naw, i want like something small on my arm. like barbed wire or something of that nature.

well its kinda late and im dead tired so im off to bed. peace up, A-town down.

-Mark-

What up niggas'

well well well, so much to say but to tired to say it. so i will sum it up for you. spent 2 hours last night talking to anna. lots of fun. cut the grass today. had a drum lesson. watched some movies with the family. thought about going to the gym, but my body hurts to much from the past couple of days. but ill try to at least get back to it tomorrow or monday. cant let my membership go to waste.

well its getting late and its about my bed time. Mueller Out

-M-

What up homies!!!

Wow 3 parties in 2 nights. how eventful have my days been. wednesday night i went over to abbotts house and partied hardy till about 2:30 in the morning then i crashed on his bed and spent the day with him yesterday. after that i went to the gym and pumped some iron. my legs are killing me from that. then last night my boss threw a graduation party at his house for me and another guy that i work with. then from there i went back to abbotts house and partied more. i stayed at abbotts house till about 12 last night then came home and went to bed.

this morning i slept till about 10 because of all the great late nights that ive been having. the great thing is im gonna do it all again tonight most likely. but for right now i have to go get ready for the work place. leave me some messages that say how much you love me.

-M-

Wow what a great weekend. staying up late, going out all the time, not eating anything cause im lazy and dont want to make anything. it was awesome. i fell asleep at like 9:30 last night. thats why there is no update for yesterday. im actually surprised that im up this late tonight. i thought i would conk out at like 9. well thats about all i have to say. weird for me i know. leave me some lovin'. Night All!!!!

Hey everybody!!!

i am in such a great mood :) i haven't felt this good in a LONG time. my weekend has been awesome and its all thanks to my great friends. i love those guys and gals to death. church on friday was so much fun. anna came with me and afterward we went out for some coffee and talked and had a fantabulous time. saturday was a drag cause i had to work all day, but after work, guess what, more anna. i went over to her house and had dinner with her family. i wasnt sure how that would go, but it went really good. after dinner we went to the park and swung on the swings and walked around having great conversation the whole time.

i am dead tired because i have had all of 8 hours sleep this whole weekend. half the dogs fault, half my fault. but i will have to sleep later because right now i am going to see Star Wars for the second time. Have a good day kiddies.

PEACE OUT !!!!!!!!!!!

AHH!!!! another day acomplished. so my day in The Rock of Mount went good. i got me some surf sandals from the Pacific Sunwear store. one black pair and one kackie pair. i sound like a girl now. all giddy about my new foot wear. BLAH!!!!!! but it is exciting though cause i got 2 pair for 25 dollars. one pair was 23 in themselves!!!!!!!! so i got one pair for like 2 bucks!!!!! its great!! im happy about my new foot wear.

oh yeah, anna is coming home tomorrow so that makes me happy. i get to see her hopefully. and even more hopefully we will get to hang out and go to dinner or lunch or coffee or just something. i have no clue what we are gonna do, but it will be awesome cause its with her. so im excited about that.

i also have church tomorrow night, and that will be fun. i will get to hang out with some people i dont get to see that often.

then on saturday after work i am going to a memorial day party at a co workers house. its gonna be good.

since i have such a jam packed weekend i am turning in for the night. oh and the reason i have a jam packed weekend is because i have the house to myself :-) WOO HOO!!!!!!!!! so if you want to do something this weekend give me a buzz. nighty night kids!!

so i just got done watching the season finales to Lost and Alias. talk about tense. i cant believe i have to wait till the fall to find out what happens in both shows. im so like whoa. thats the only way i know how to explain it. i cant explain it any other way.

now other than Lost and Alias, my day went really good. dont know why, it just did. i am doing so much better now. i feel like i could take on the world. my mood and attitude are like through the roof. i look forward to the next day now. i actually want to get out of bed instead of staying curled up in a ball crying. my outlook has totally changed since sunday night.

tomorrow i have a nice full day planned. since i dont have to work me and my mom and sister are going to rocky mount to do some browsing and shopping. Pac Sun baby, yeah!! i love me some Pac Sun. i could live in that store. they are the perfect store for an emo boy like me. can you say card it!!! since i get to go to RM tomorrow i am going to bed cause i have no clue when mom wants to get out of here in the morning.

have a great night kids. ;)

ok so its tuesday and i already want the weekend to be here. i dont know why. i mean i have to work saturday, so i dont know whats up. i guess it might be because anna is coming back from camp in SC for the weekend and we are hopefully gonna hang out. she is one cool chick. i think im starting to like her a little bit too. i mean she is great. everything that she has been through in her life has given her such a strong personality. everything has a good side to it, with her there is never a bad side. whats even better is that she is such a strong christian and thats one thing i look for first in a person. plus she is really cute and thats always a good thing. i really want to hang with her this weekend. so hopefully that will happen.

well i have a long day tomorrow and i need my sleep. night night kids

ok so my day went a whole lot better today. i was alot happier and plus i got to see my emmy marfa!!! i love me some emily. she always makes me feel better. i cant wait till tomorrow when i get to see her again. another reason i am doing better is because i got to bang on the drums. that really gets out your aggression. its GREAT!!!!!!!! me and abbott really rocked out tonight. major chevelle tonight. abbott had a couple slash moments which were really funny. we both just all of the sudden bust out into 2 totally different things and it sounded like crap, but it was oh so much fun. i cant wait till i get my new drums. its gonna be great. they will sound so much better than the pieces of crap i have now. only a little more time before they come! ok so i dont have much to write about tonight so im gonna go to bed now. have a good night everybody!!!

<FONT color=#009900>Why do i torture myself over a stupid girl???? can anybody tell me why?? i'm killing myself trying to figure everything out and i dont know why. well you know what, i am officially done. im not gonna worry about it. its over and done with now. im moving on and i dont care if i hurt anyone in the process. well since my day sucked im going to bed early. g'night</FONT>

ok so my day was a little bit more exciting today. thins morning i had a drum lesson, which i really ned to work on alot of stuff cause i really havent been playing all that much. so needless to say i need to work alot more now. then i had to cut the grass. after that i got a showercause i stunk!! then i had to go to a PARTY for shannon rogers. it was a great party. i met a whole lot of cool new people. the party went from 5 to like 9:30 then moved over to books-a-million till 11 when we had to leave cause they were closing. the two people that i met tonight that i really liked were anna and erin. they had to be two of the coolest people there. i got to know them really well and i think i have two new friends :) yay me!!! anyway, i have to get up early tomorrow for two church services so i am going to bed, night kiddies.

nothing really exciting happened today. well i did almost get a fox for a pet!!! that was pretty awesome. we got a new animal at work too. a russian glass lizard. pretty sweet. i have no idea where i am gonna put it though cause we have no space what-so-ever. oh well its a pretty cool creature.
ta-ta for now

ok so i didnt post yesterday because my day was very busy and i didnt get home till like 3 in the morning, which i'll explain later. for right now let me start at the begining of the day.

so i wake up and im feeling good because of the night before at chick-fil-a. so i go off to work and im doing really good. after work i had to go to church to help set up sound and props for a play that the little kiddies were putting on. i was fine until i look back at the back doors of the gymshuary (the sanctuary has been moved into the gym while they are renovating it)and there walking in is my ex girlfriend allison. right then my stomach lurched and my heart dropped. not because i cant stand her, but because im still deeply in love with her and she doesnt want to have anything to do with me. its horrible. i know she still loves me too and she wants to be together, but for some reason she cant be with me. i dont know why because she never talked to me when we were dating. for some reason she could never express her feelings. she cannot communicate what-so-ever. and that always killed me. anyway, so she walked in and i all of the sudden became nauseous. so i put on that happy face so that no one can see how bad i feel and go about my work and kinda watch her out of the corner of my eye. she looks just about as bad as i feel. i wanted to talk to her so bad, but i knew if i did i would say something stupid or just dig my hole deeper because i keep trying to fix things and i mean them all for good, but everything i try to fix just gets screwed up more and im getting tired of it. so im trying to move on and thats why i gave the girl at chick-fil-a my number. apparently its not working though because i still think of allison all the time and it hurts so bad that all i want to do is curl up in a ball in my bed and cry for the rest of my pitiful life. its very sad. i wanted to talk to her the whole night though and i was glad when the whole thing was over so i could get out of there. after church i went over to my youth leaders house to meet him so we could go to the midnight showing of star wars!!!! thats why i didnt get home till 3 in the morning. the movie was awesome by the way. so i went home to bed and luckily i didnt have to work today so i got to sleep in. 

today i pretty much did nothing. it was great!!! i watched tv all morning, which i never get to do. this afternoon i went hung with abbott at his house for a while. after that i came home and watched more tv. tons of fun.

so the past two days have been pretty eventful. now i am going to go to bed so i will be able to get up for work tomorrow. night kiddies!! ;)

What is Your Star Wars Horoscope?


Star Wars Horoscope for Sagittarius


You are superbly wise and have been known to spread your wisdom widely.
You are impatient and pushy when people take your teachings too lightly.
And your philosophical side always peeks through.

Star wars character you are most like: Yoda

 

 

Just thought this was friggin' Awesome!!!!!

ok so i went to chick-fil-a after bible study with my good buddies abbott and joseph and we tormented the staff there. i went through the drive-thru to get a refill for my drink and walked back in the resturant and everyone was like what??? the reason i went through the drive-thru was because this hot girl was working there and i wanted to hit on her. i kept trying to get her number, but she wouldnt give it to me. so i finally got one of those comment cards and was like "so i want to let 'chick-fil-a' know what i think about the service here" and i filled out the card and gave it to her and was like "so do you think 'headquarters' will give me a call about my comments". she was like "you probably wont get a call, but you might get an email". it sounds really childish, but it was great fun. it was GREAT!!!!!

well kiddos it is time for me to retire for the night because i am tired and there is much needed rest to be had. so until tomorrow i bid you ado.

Peace

Mark
